{"tid":2429693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘇惠德：若今日未完成程序明天再續　料明天傍晚有決定","createTime":"2021-03-02T13:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T13:29:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29c4e9d4858a7fc27c17906f556d4313e44f1a87","tid":2429693,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:19:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578378-20210302.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578378-20210302.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=e052729a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578378-20210302.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5ba0de76\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578378-20210302.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n47名發起或參與去年民主派初選人士，被控「串謀顛覆國家政權罪」，案件一連兩日提堂，至晚上繼續審訊，預料案件將延至明天。<br />\n<br />\n國安法指定法官蘇惠德晚上約7時安排暫時休庭，讓控辯雙方及被告用膳。至晚上近8時恢復審訊，繼續進行餘下被告的保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n蘇惠德早前說，今日的審訊時間最多可能直至晚上10時。有被告代表律師在晚膳後一開庭就指出，從書記得知，仍有15名被告的程序未處理，認為今日餘下時間要處理眾人保釋申請有困難。<br />\n<br />\n蘇惠德回應說，若今日未能完成有關程序，將於明天再續，估計明天下午會聽完陳詞，預料明天傍晚有決定。"},{"pid":"f3d8fbee963ef62d5199265c57c7403055f11e8a","tid":2429693,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:20:21.000Z","msg":"馬拉松審訊至多名被告暈倒送院<br />\n<br />\n算唔算酷刑?"},{"pid":"6bd53ff3fac27f9df9998b2b50db162df408001d","tid":2429693,"uid":389554,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:21:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2efa27c9c2150eefad7c418007d8cf78fc84e2d","tid":2429693,"uid":67160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bd53ff3fac27f9df9998b2b50db162df408001d","tid":2429693,"uid":389554,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f3d8fbee963ef62d5199265c57c7403055f11e8a","tid":2429693,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2